        "id": 1398165
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-02-05T21:32:18Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I was misled and thought all PermDenied errors are on Py top-level.That\u0027s why I decided to convert them to Go individual-level. But then I found out some PermDenied is on Py individual-level today. We should fix that bug in Py and here we can make them all to Go top-level errs. see more detail on the reply in batch_test.go, L375.",
      "parentUuid": "8a17c861_2cf568cf",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 124,
        "startChar": 2,
        "endLine": 132,
        "endChar": 3
      },
